summary: Small player home located just outside of Riverwood.
descriptionHtml:
Small player home located just outside of Riverwood. Contains several mannequins, weapon racks and plaques, Crafting and Enchanting tables, and plenty of storage room with a great view of Skyrimâ€™s best town. Includes a hidden sanctuary in the basement with even more storage.


Originally made just for me but I am such a nice guy I decided to share it with the world. Lucky you. Enjoy!

Edit: Update finally uploaded! Fixed some bugs with floors and the navmesh on the deck as well as giving it an overall more polished feel. Hurrah.

Edit: Added a tanning rack and grinding wheel to the house
